[{"index":53,"title":"回复：回复：【原创】苍茫","content":"哇咔...LS头像好有爱&gt;v&lt;~","author":"ㄗs崩潰","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.ec9ccd24.cuLXh91xYg_HgiUkfkPLhg&fr=pb","date":"2009-07-18 08:47","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":"https://imgsa.baidu.com/%D6%ED%D6%EDde%D0%A1%CE%DD/mpic/item/28c2017f8cb83d2a28388aaa.jpg?v=tbs"},{"index":54,"title":"回复：回复：【原创】苍茫","content":"在说我么？本人大名J博士哦","author":"j89121234","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.179a5dd.48qCdXXk5Gc0oVnCzky50A&fr=pb","date":"2009-07-18 08:50","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":55,"title":"回复：回复：【原创】苍茫","content":"“我不知道，可能他们觉得我没有利用价值了，不过夷阳的情报我是一点也没有泄露。”<br><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 秦微将军咳了一声，脸上的笑容更加明显了：“就算你说的是真的，我们对另一件事也同样感兴趣，那就是你的身份。” 秦微把手中的档案递给我说，“你看看这是不是你的档案？”<br><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 我拿到手里一看，果然是自己的档案，上面注明了我的身份和入军时间，还有一些其他信息，和我当年为混入亚京军而伪造的个人资料果然相同。我大致浏览了一下后交还给秦微。<br><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; “据我们推算你的入军时间是在宣夷皇帝被刺杀的三个月后，而这三个月我们一直在追查宣夷族两个在逃皇子的下落。”秦微继续说，“后来我们才知道与亚京军交锋的革命军首领竟是宣夷的大皇子，因此我们猜想二皇子也许就隐藏在亚京军中，特别有可能在殖民地地区。你说是不是啊？慎风少尉。”<br><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 不得不承认他的推理确实很有道理，当年真是小看他了，不过我仍然是自信满满的，要是我的计划能够顺利的话，赢的人还是我。我忍不住略带嘲笑地问他：“你认为二皇子是谁呢？”<br><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; “就是你，慎风少尉。” 秦微厉声说，“三年前当你知道了革命军首领就是你哥哥时，为了掩盖身份继续留在殖民军卧底，你不惜杀死你的亲哥哥，正如你所愿，凌芜战役后总部对你的怀疑有所减少，但是这一次你是跑不掉了，因为我们手里有证明你身份的重要证据。”\u0018","author":"幻灭之尘","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.9edf9a0a.rfXLTL3kf8i5QNypvTEXuw&fr=pb","date":"2009-07-18 09:10","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":56,"title":"回复：回复：【原创】苍茫","content":"...博...博士  = =|||&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;  ","author":"ㄗs崩潰","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.ec9ccd24.cuLXh91xYg_HgiUkfkPLhg&fr=pb","date":"2009-07-18 09:32","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":"https://imgsa.baidu.com/timelees1125/mpic/item/61a31f3fe931f81f71cf6c74.jpg?v=tbs"},{"index":57,"title":"回复：回复：【原创】苍茫","content":"<img class=\"BDE_Smiley\" height=\"40\" src=\"http://tieba.baidu.com/tb/editor/images/jd/j_0009.gif\" width=\"40\" changedsize=\"false\"><img class=\"BDE_Smiley\" height=\"40\" src=\"http://tieba.baidu.com/tb/editor/images/jd/j_0009.gif\" width=\"40\" changedsize=\"false\"><img class=\"BDE_Smiley\" height=\"40\" src=\"http://tieba.baidu.com/tb/editor/images/jd/j_0009.gif\" width=\"40\" changedsize=\"false\">博士！！！\u0018","author":"幻灭之尘","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.9edf9a0a.rfXLTL3kf8i5QNypvTEXuw&fr=pb","date":"2009-07-18 20:34","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":"https://imgsa.baidu.com/%C1%F9%C3%A2%BB%C3%B3%BE/pic/item/eaa2b3cc5cf3023101e928af.jpeg?v=tbs"},{"index":58,"title":"回复：回复：【原创】苍茫","content":"倒水的路过","author":"幻灭之尘","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.9edf9a0a.rfXLTL3kf8i5QNypvTEXuw&fr=pb","date":"2009-07-19 16:19","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":59,"title":"回复：回复：【原创】苍茫","content":"我静静听着他的叙述，暗笑他有一点没有想到，杀死原总督的人也是我。<br><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 秦微从怀里掏出一个紫色手环递给我说：“这就是宣夷皇子象征，你看看是不是你的。”<br><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 我拿起手环仔细的看了看，果然是母后的遗物，一点也不奇怪，我早就知道那天肯定是璃若偷走的，只是没想到幕后指使人居然是他。我知道是瞒不过了，于是便承认了自己的身份。<br><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 秦微走到我跟前说：“我们要把你立即押送到总部。”这时玄光门打开了，从外面进来了两个要把我带走的士兵。<br><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; “等等，秦微将军。”鸿贽大人站起身说，“还是先把他软禁在这里吧，相信总部那边也不会那么快得知这个消息的。”<br><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; “可是……总督大人。”<br><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; “就这么定了，不用担心我会处理好的。再说天蛮军的进攻可能就在今晚，先应付好敌人吧。”<br><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 秦微没了理由，只得吩咐手下把我带到软禁的房间。临走时我偷看了一眼鸿贽，他面无表情的看着我。<br><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 鸿贽，你果然还是站在我这边的，宣夷反攻的希望就要靠你了,我心里微笑着离开。\u0018","author":"幻灭之尘","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.9edf9a0a.rfXLTL3kf8i5QNypvTEXuw&fr=pb","date":"2009-07-19 16:23","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":60,"title":"回复：回复：【原创】苍茫","content":".......","author":"幻灭之尘","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.9edf9a0a.rfXLTL3kf8i5QNypvTEXuw&fr=pb","date":"2009-07-20 11:28","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":"https://imgsa.baidu.com/%C1%F9%C3%A2%BB%C3%B3%BE/pic/item/eaa2b3cc5cf3023101e928af.jpeg?v=tbs"},{"index":61,"title":"回复：回复：【原创】苍茫","content":"不错..很有爱..","author":"甜蜜de猪猪","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.d52ea5a8.DSNW4EcdqgOpaMIQefalnA&fr=pb","date":"2009-07-20 16:10","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":"https://imgsa.baidu.com/%D6%ED%D6%EDde%D0%A1%CE%DD/mpic/item/662956cf7d123019f9dc616a.jpg?v=tbs"},{"index":62,"title":"回复：回复：【原创】苍茫","content":"<img class=\"BDE_Smiley\" height=\"40\" src=\"http://tieba.baidu.com/tb/editor/images/jd/j_0012.gif\" width=\"40\" changedsize=\"false\">","author":"幻灭之尘","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.9edf9a0a.rfXLTL3kf8i5QNypvTEXuw&fr=pb","date":"2009-07-20 22:35","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":"https://imgsa.baidu.com/%C1%F9%C3%A2%BB%C3%B3%BE/pic/item/eaa2b3cc5cf3023101e928af.jpeg?v=tbs"},{"index":64,"title":"回复：回复：【原创】苍茫","content":"这时整个天际都被强烈的光线笼罩着，爆炸声和叫喊声交织在一起，看来天蛮军开始攻击夷阳了。<br><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 卓缃站在“苍茫”号前，她的眼色渐渐从蓝色变成了绿色。我突然恍然大悟，是眼色遮蔽剂的作用，原来她不是亚京人而是和我一样的宣夷人。<br><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 不过眼色遮蔽剂只有三个小时的作用，看来哥哥开始行动了，他准备在天蛮军和亚京军交锋之际用异能离合炮消灭所有人。<br><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 望着“苍茫”号驾驶舱外熊熊燃烧的战火，我不禁问卓缃：“我们这是要去哪？”<br><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; “离开阎星。”卓缃继续驾驶着战舰，在下面是几栋在燃烧的居民楼。<br><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; “难道你打算不负责任的离开家乡去苍茫的宇宙吗？”<br><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 卓缃突然狠狠地抓着我的衣领说：“听着，总督大人救你是为了让你活命，所以我不会送你去华炎的。”<br><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; “假如这是一场被设计的战争呢？你还会希望有人无辜的死去吗？” <br><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 沉默了片刻，卓缃无奈地说：“信你一次吧，就算我破例违命。”她微笑着改变了航向。\u0018","author":"幻灭之尘","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.9edf9a0a.rfXLTL3kf8i5QNypvTEXuw&fr=pb","date":"2009-07-22 16:07","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":65,"title":"回复：回复：【原创】苍茫","content":"up~","author":"116.17.10.*","author_link":null,"date":"2009-07-23 11:29","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":66,"title":"回复：回复：【原创】苍茫","content":"up~D啊","author":"116.17.2.*","author_link":null,"date":"2009-07-24 09:14","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":68,"title":"回复：回复：【原创】苍茫","content":"SF~~","author":"薇熏香蝶","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.7da1cd26.ncgd8hsuEBf2nM6_SvCQRw&fr=pb","date":"2009-07-25 12:29","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":69,"title":"回复：回复：【原创】苍茫","content":"学渺的~~~ 自顶~up","author":"116.17.13.*","author_link":null,"date":"2009-07-26 08:06","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":70,"title":"回复：回复：【原创】苍茫","content":"再次自顶~~没人回我就更文了<img class=\"BDE_Smiley\" height=\"40\" src=\"http://tieba.baidu.com/tb/editor/images/jd/j_0006.gif\" width=\"40\" changedsize=\"false\">","author":"幻灭之尘","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.9edf9a0a.rfXLTL3kf8i5QNypvTEXuw&fr=pb","date":"2009-07-27 21:37","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":"https://imgsa.baidu.com/476371702/pic/item/5eba7c134ba56f74f919b8d0.jpeg?v=tbs"},{"index":71,"title":"回复：回复：【原创】苍茫","content":"（尾声）<br><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 璃若缓缓地走向一座没有名字的墓碑，并献上了一簇花圈。今天的夜晚异常寂静，她沐浴在微风中，闭目沉思，体味这少有的寂静。<br><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 她身后的中年男子同样向墓碑献上了花圈，他依然记得三个月前自己头上这片天空是血红色的。<br><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; “鸿贽大人，你不觉得获得胜利是一件很开心的事吗？” 璃若笑道。<br><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; “开心的只有统治者吧。” 鸿贽淡淡笑道，“这片土地不是我们的，只要宣夷族继续存在在这个星球上，他们就一定会设法夺回这片土地。”<br><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 鸿贽继续看着天，他的眼睛渐渐变成了绿色。`（全文完）\u0018","author":"幻灭之尘","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.9edf9a0a.rfXLTL3kf8i5QNypvTEXuw&fr=pb","date":"2009-07-30 10:22","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":"https://imgsa.baidu.com/%C1%F9%C3%A2%BB%C3%B3%BE/pic/item/eaa2b3cc5cf3023101e928af.jpeg?v=tbs"}]